title: Under Sorrow
body:
by stigmascontrol

A facility full of anxious students. A corrupted environment learning to become the next generation’s perfect society. Kim Taehyung is one amongst many students who has lived captive in this facility his whole life. Seeing fellow students murdering each other, seeing staff members shooting students for misbehavior, later becoming the meat that the students feast on.
Never seeing the world outside. Who knows what lies beyond these walls. There may be chaos in the outside world, a black void, even more death amongst humans.
All Kim Taehyung wants is to seek a companion that will stay by his side. However, in this world of his, a concept such as that does not exist. Only fear and constant anxiety fills one’s mind.
One day, a transfer student appears before him. A strange boy. Who is this boy?
